Title: Circe
Writer: Manuel Antin, Julio Cortázar, Héctor Grossi
Actors: Graciela Borges, Raúl Aubel, Alberto Argibay, Alberto Barcel
Plot: Delia Mañara is notorious in her quarter of Buenos Aires for the mysterious deaths of two of her fiancés. She lives in a twilight world and gains most satisfaction through the exercise of power over others.
